                                <Label Text="Wow!! I still to these days love this movie!! It has a great choice of cast, and a strong storyline. Definitely worth a watch! I do recommend this movie to anybody. Five stars across the board!!!&#10;" TextColor="#37383b" FontSize="15" CharacterSpacing="0.2" />

