                                    <Image Source="https://i.ibb.co/Bs7bnky/5.png" WidthRequest="70"/>
                                </StackLayout>
                                <Label Text="I love this movie so much. My dad showed it to me a few years ago and I have watched it 5 times since then. It is creative and hilarious. It is for sure my favorite comedy. It has everything you want in a comedy: good jokes, creative writing, and a great cast. Just if you haven't seen it yet please do. I guarantee you will enjoy yourself. &#10;" TextColor="#37383b" FontSize="15" CharacterSpacing="0.2" />

                                <StackLayout Orientation="Horizontal" Spacing="10">
