                                    <Label Text="jake scott &#10;a year ago " FontAttributes="Bold" TextColor="Black" FontSize="13" CharacterSpacing="0.5"/>
                                    <Image Source="https://i.ibb.co/7XwtYVb/4.png" WidthRequest="70"/>
                                </StackLayout>
                                <Label Text="A very funny comedy that is raunchy, unique and is extremely engaging. One of this films biggest strengths is it's script and the way it's characters pull the dialogue off the page.Aside from pacing issues in between the second and third act, as well as a few story lines that are forgotten completely in the mix, this is a very well made comedy.4/5  &#10;" TextColor="#37383b" FontSize="15" CharacterSpacing="0.2" />

                                <StackLayout Orientation="Horizontal" Spacing="10">
                                    <Image Source="https://i.ibb.co/HTKDnKz/person-icon.png" HeightRequest="40"/>
                                    <Label Text="Mihika Bharathan &#10;a year ago" FontAttributes="Bold" TextColor="Black" FontSize="13" CharacterSpacing="0.5"/>
                                    <Image Source="https://i.ibb.co/Bs7bnky/5.png" WidthRequest="70"/>
                                </StackLayout>
                                <Label Text="Probably the BEST FILM FRANCHISE I've EVER come across ❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️. I love how the story connects and flows from part 1 all the way till part 3. Great beginning and an amazing end to the story. A classic movie 👏👏👏👏. 10/10&#10;" TextColor="#37383b" FontSize="15" CharacterSpacing="0.2" />

                                <StackLayout Orientation="Horizontal" Spacing="10">
                                    <Image Source="https://i.ibb.co/HTKDnKz/person-icon.png" HeightRequest="40"/>
                                    <Label Text="Mrityunjay Sharma &#10;a year ago" FontAttributes="Bold" TextColor="Black" FontSize="13" CharacterSpacing="0.5"/>
                                    <Image Source="https://i.ibb.co/5v61tGY/3-stars.png" WidthRequest="70"/>
                                </StackLayout>
                                <Label Text="I watch a lot of movies, but only a few have the charm to impress me. This is NOT the one. I felt the plot is over-exaggerated and far away from being realistic. True be honest, it's a movie for the kids(ofc excluding explicit content). Hangover movie is so overrated! In the end, it just okayish 5/10. An average time-pass movie.&#10;" TextColor="#37383b" FontSize="15" CharacterSpacing="0.2" />

                                <StackLayout Orientation="Horizontal" Spacing="10">
                                    <Image Source="https://i.ibb.co/HTKDnKz/person-icon.png" HeightRequest="40"/>
                                    <Label Text="Salvia Salmon &#10;a month ago " FontAttributes="Bold" TextColor="Black" FontSize="13" CharacterSpacing="0.5"/>
